data.description: Amazing residence nestled in the highly coveted School District 20, situated in the esteemed Northfork at Briargate community. This home has an array of desirable features. Upon entry, you're greeted by an abundance of natural light that illuminates the wood flooring adorning the main level. The versatile layout effortlessly accommodates various lifestyles, with a formal dining room that seamlessly transitions into a formal living room, or a spacious home office. The heart of the home lies in the expansive kitchen, eating area, and family room, designed to facilitate effortless entertaining and socializing. The family room exudes warmth and charm with its gas fireplace and incredible windows, inviting the outdoors in while providing a cozy ambiance. The kitchen is contemporary, featuring white cabinets, sleek grey quartz countertops, and a generously sized pantry, ensuring both style and functionality. Upstairs features three bedrooms, two baths, a versatile loft space, and a large conveniently located laundry room. Luxurious touches abound, including wood laminate flooring in the loft and stairway landings. The basement provides even more living space, with nine-foot ceilings accentuating the sense of openness. Two additional bedrooms, a bathroom, and a family room complete this level, offering ample space. Conveniently located within walking distance to Pine Creek and a brand new elementary school, offering swift access to Powers and the I-25 corridor.
